		<div class="post-2677 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-copyleft category-copywrong category-free-culture category-the-interwebs" id="post-2677">


<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/09/28/is-chinese-video-hosting-the-answer/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Is Chinese video hosting the answer?">Is Chinese video hosting the answer?</a></h2>
		</div>

