		<div class="post-2483 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-copyleft category-copywrong category-free-culture category-law category-new-york category-speaking" id="post-2483">


<div class="post-headline">		<h2>			
			<a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/05/12/intellectual-disobedience/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Intellectual Disobedience">Intellectual Disobedience</a></h2>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p><iframe width="640" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/dfGWQnj6RNA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
<p>A little talk I gave about <em>Seder-Masochism</em>-in-progress and Civil Disobedience at Brooklyn Law School&#8217;s &#8220;Legal Hackathon&#8221; several weeks ago.</p>
<div class="plus-one-wrap"><g:plusone href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/05/12/intellectual-disobedience/"></g:plusone></div><div class="addtoany_share_save_container"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="wpa2a_23"><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save" style="background:url(http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/favicon.png) no-repeat scroll 4px 0px !important;padding:0 0 0 25px;display:inline-block;height:16px;vertical-align:middle">Share/Bookmark</a></div></div><p class="wp-flattr-button"><a class="FlattrButton" style="display:none;" href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/05/12/intellectual-disobedience/" title=" Intellectual Disobedience" rev="flattr;uid:ninapaley;language:en_GB;category:text;tags:blog;button:compact;">A little talk I gave about Seder-Masochism-in-progress and Civil Disobedience at Brooklyn Law School&#8217;s &#8220;Legal Hackathon&#8221; several weeks ago. Share/Bookmark</a></p></div>

<div class="post-footer">May 12th, 2012 |  Category: <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copyleft/" title="View all posts in copyleft" rel="category tag">copyleft</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/copywrong/" title="View all posts in copywrong" rel="category tag">copywrong</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/free-culture/" title="View all posts in Free Culture" rel="category tag">Free Culture</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/law/" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/new-york/" title="View all posts in New York" rel="category tag">New York</a>, <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/category/speaking/" title="View all posts in speaking" rel="category tag">speaking</a> | <a href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2012/05/12/intellectual-disobedience/#comments" class="comments-link"  title="Comment on Intellectual Disobedience">10 comments</a> </div>
